author: John King
title: Video shows man grabbing gun from suspect in S.F. home invasion
text: Here’s something you don’t see often: A robber pulls a gun on a man in the man’s garage, they struggle, the victim wrests the gun away from the assailant — and it’s all captured on the home security camera.
